{"title":"乡村风景线","authors":["朱谷忠"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":2,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡村风景线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱谷忠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农技问讯处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青蒲编翠篱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芦竹架屋梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农技站的问讯处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"设在圩市上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人，拥拥挤挤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声，闹闹嚷嚷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问风问雨问节气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问水问肥问土壤……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新鲜的课题，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多穗的幻想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一一详聊细解答，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切胜过拉家常……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋后土礼品堆满屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你推我搡汗直淌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢你？感谢我？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿，多亏县委支持、街道帮忙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豆腐村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瓦房落柳丛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电磨唱新韵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门前道路通八方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六七家人集一“村”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酱豆腐——甜丝丝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸豆腐——香喷喷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一批：去赶早市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一批：供应预订。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日转月转磨盘转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风传水唱“豆腐村”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨尽暗淡旧年岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨出如画新光景！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}